data.description: Step into the epitome of luxury living with this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2219 square foot pool home nestled on a coveted corner lot in the prestigious Arlington subdivision. Radiating a perfect harmony of comfort and style, the open floor plan welcomes you with vaulted ceilings in the formal living and dining areas, creating an immediate sense of spacious elegance. The well-designed kitchen, a hub for entertaining, seamlessly connects to a cozy family room, perfect for creating cherished memories with loved ones.  Sunlight bathes the living spaces through large sliders in the breakfast area, dining room, and master bedroom, all leading to the lanai. Revel in a home filled with warmth and natural light. The split floor plan ensures the owner's privacy with walk-in closets, blending comfort and functionality seamlessly. Step outside into your private oasis on an oversized corner lot that offers both privacy and a sparkling heated pool and spa with upgraded equipment, perfect for relaxation or entertaining.  This home boasts recent upgrades for your peace of mind and convenience. The HVAC was replaced in 2016, ensuring energy efficiency and climate control, while the Roof has been recently renewed in 2015, guaranteeing longevity. Nestled in the sought-after Arlington subdivision, this property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, schools, parks, and more. Seize the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a viewing today and envision a life of luxury and comfort in this Arlington gem.
